timing_extract_model_write_lvf(25.10)    timing_extract_model_write_lvf(25.10)

Name
       timing_extract_model_write_lvf

Syntax
       timing_extract_model_write_lvf {true | false}

       Default: false

       Generates  extracted  timing  model  (ETM) containing Liberty Variation
       Format (LVF) model.

       When set to true, this global variable enables  writing  separate  mean
       and  variation  tables  for all the delay/constraint and transition ta-
       bles.

       When set to false, the variation data will be merged with the mean val-
       ues. The mean +/- nsigma  values  of  delay/constraint/transition  data
       will be written in the ETM.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

